name: No More Sadness hahahahaha....
description: I imagine how if the series of Jackass became everyone's habit. Yes maybe from some you may just see it as a violent scene, but look at the players are all having fun. They are hurt and hurt without any resentment as if the malice no longer exists, all just having fun. All filled with jokes and laughter there was no intention to kill each other. Isn't that what everyone wants, yes it's joy.   No good? Wait a minute if you say it's no good why those players can have a good relationship. Maybe we're the only ones who can't understand them.
